snippet.title: ESJ2 Aug9th
snippet.description:
Brutal Hardcore Platforming + Stylish Electronic Beats, a Thicc-as-all-hell sequel to the original game. 

Steal butts, earn Daddy's love and murder Santa, in this sensational new platforming game.
